org.jpws.pwslib.data

Class HeaderFieldList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jpws.pwslib.data.RawFieldList
      • org.jpws.pwslib.data.HeaderFieldList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class HeaderFieldList
extends RawFieldList
    A descendant of RawFieldList that limits the range of valid elements to field types 0..254 and supplies additional functionality specific to header-field lists. Furthermore, the methods of this class are synchronised.
